WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.493
Well, good morning, evening, and afternoon wherever you are.

00:00:04.493 --> 00:00:07.560
I guess thank you for joining me tonight.

00:00:07.773 --> 00:00:10.620
I have some things on my heart to talk to you all about.

00:00:11.304 --> 00:00:18.834
It was really cool today; the Lord spoke to me when I was at the sandwich shop getting a turkey sandwich.

00:00:19.137 --> 00:00:27.440
The Lord spoke to me when I was in the sandwich shop today with the lady with the pink hair.

00:00:27.636 --> 00:00:29.004
So, I'm going to go over that.

00:00:29.004 --> 00:00:32.747
I'll go over what the Lord showed me in the spirit.

00:00:32.991 --> 00:00:40.835
I was sitting there praying like I always do, praying over the people making my food because I don't know who's touching it.

00:00:41.120 --> 00:00:46.950
I was just praying over it all, and the Lord opened my eyes in the spirit and I saw some things.

00:00:47.570 --> 00:00:53.731
I'll get into that, but we'll go over what we saw yesterday concerning Katy Perry.

00:00:54.269 --> 00:00:58.655
The Lord has His hand on that.

00:00:59.210 --> 00:01:17.540
I saw she's made some very bad choices, and the decision she made was to go down the secular path, but it was a demonic front that was on this lady.

00:01:26.711 --> 00:01:28.609
I don't even know how old she is, but the Lord was showing me that there's a pull on her, and we're going to keep praying.

00:01:30.093 --> 00:01:34.027
I believe God, and this is what I think is interesting.

00:01:34.027 --> 00:01:37.400
The Lord showed us Kanye West.

00:01:42.350 --> 00:01:43.927
He showed us Justin last night.

00:01:47.160 --> 00:01:47.790
He showed us Katy Perry.

00:01:47.790 --> 00:01:51.608
And then who else did He show last night?

00:01:51.608 --> 00:01:51.896
Oh, and country music.

00:01:51.896 --> 00:02:12.830
He said, 'There is about to be something with country music that's going to be a major revival in that arena of music where you would see country music stars really get radical for Jesus in the days ahead, even more than some who are riding the fence a little bit, probably.

00:02:12.830 --> 00:02:15.926
But there are some radical ones.

00:02:15.926 --> 00:02:23.120
' What I'm going to say goes alongside what the Lord showed us last night in prayer.

00:02:49.345 --> 00:02:49.580
The wind's blowing—hopefully, that's not a distraction.

00:02:49.580 --> 00:02:52.720
You can turn that off; that's really loud.

00:02:52.720 --> 00:03:01.785
As I was sitting there waiting at the sandwich shop at Jimmy John's, I was praying in the spirit over my food.

00:03:03.590 --> 00:03:05.885
I could see the girl's bright pink hair above the counter.

00:03:06.275 --> 00:03:09.244
I kept looking, praying for her and interceding.

00:03:09.244 --> 00:03:24.165
All of a sudden, the Lord opened my eyes and I saw music notes flowing up out of me because I was humming a tune, a song.

00:03:26.469 --> 00:03:31.840
These music notes started turning like a whirlwind.

00:03:32.116 --> 00:03:37.867
As they were going in a whirlwind, I could see the notes and the lines of all the music.

00:03:38.453 --> 00:03:41.920
It almost looked like a cartoon vision; the music was dancing.

00:03:51.107 --> 00:04:01.913
As I was singing and humming this song, the Lord said, 'Brandon, you're about to see something that we've never seen before concerning music.

00:04:01.913 --> 00:04:11.000
' He said that it's always been about the devil's crowd and the music they've put out for decades.

00:04:11.000 --> 00:04:19.239
Everybody talks about what the secular music industry is putting out, but He said He was reversing the status quo.

00:04:21.600 --> 00:04:26.914
The status quo of how the music industry has always been is changing.

00:04:28.080 --> 00:04:34.113
He said there is new heavenly music like we've never heard before.

00:04:37.680 --> 00:04:52.213
As I was looking in the spirit, He said, 'Brandon, Satan has his own demonic influence over music because that's what he was created for.

00:04:52.213 --> 00:04:54.960
' He was created for worship.

00:04:59.413 --> 00:05:08.840
Lucifer was created with all the music coming up out of him for the worship of the Father.

00:05:08.840 --> 00:05:15.331
But he turned to Satan, and of course, as he fell, everything went bad.

00:05:15.331 --> 00:05:21.190
But that talent is still on him to bring in worldly music that sucks you in.

00:05:24.804 --> 00:05:27.844
A lot of secular music has a pull; it gets you in moods and changes atmospheres.

00:05:31.417 --> 00:05:34.720
There's a pull to the music, which is what the Lord was showing me.

00:05:34.720 --> 00:05:47.570
But He said, 'As of today, Brandon, there's going to be an even greater pull on Christian music with a divine reversal.

00:05:47.570 --> 00:05:58.680
' A divine reversal is taking place concerning music with heavenly music and sounds that will draw them in.

00:06:03.853 --> 00:06:13.888
As I was humming a tune I'd never heard before—I can't even mimic it now, but it was beautiful—I could hear the sound from the Father humming this tune; it was angelic.

00:06:16.760 --> 00:06:18.253
I was mimicking what I was hearing in the spirit.

00:06:21.675 --> 00:06:22.895
The girl with the pink hair kept peeking over.

00:06:27.720 --> 00:06:28.040
I said, 'See how it draws?

00:06:38.660 --> 00:06:42.800
See how she's looking?

00:06:42.800 --> 00:06:46.550
' I saw her pink head peeking over the counter.

00:06:48.349 --> 00:06:57.440
I was humming—not obnoxiously, just a little hum to myself—but I could feel the anointing pulling.

00:06:57.860 --> 00:07:04.337
The Lord said, 'It draws you in, just like music is created to do.

00:07:04.337 --> 00:07:10.120
' It was a symphony and a melody; it was beautiful.

00:07:13.440 --> 00:07:13.800
I could hear heavenly sounds.

00:07:14.867 --> 00:07:16.582
The Lord told me to mimic this.

00:07:16.582 --> 00:07:24.406
I could hear it in the spirit, and as I heard Him humming, I was mimicking that sound.

00:07:24.731 --> 00:07:29.209
That young girl with the pink hair kept looking, and I could feel it.

00:07:30.440 --> 00:07:42.230
The Lord showed me that the sound coming up out of my spirit was turning and dancing, moving in the atmosphere of the sandwich shop.

00:07:42.535 --> 00:07:45.560
Can you make her stop doing that?

00:07:46.032 --> 00:07:50.020
My little girl is really up to stuff tonight.

00:07:50.020 --> 00:07:53.040
Tell her to be still while Daddy's doing this.

00:07:53.040 --> 00:07:56.070
I'm sorry, folks.

00:07:58.396 --> 00:08:07.737
The Lord showed me that the status quo is about to change concerning music.

00:08:08.251 --> 00:08:24.891
It went alongside what we saw last night about Katy Perry, Justin, country music artists, and Kanye West—how the devil has had a hold of these people and the Lord is pulling them out of the darkness.

00:08:26.560 --> 00:08:31.680
Justin Bieber is born again, but the Lord showed us a fork in the road.

00:08:31.680 --> 00:08:45.920
There are major decisions coming concerning his marriage; we are praying over his marriage because one path leads to darkness and the other to greater light.

00:08:47.124 --> 00:08:52.000
The Lord said, 'Pray for him.

00:08:52.000 --> 00:08:53.220
Pray for Justin Bieber.

00:08:53.220 --> 00:08:58.032
' I want to make sure I say it right because I don't want to butcher somebody's name.

00:08:58.544 --> 00:09:05.029
I then saw Kanye with mirrored snow goggles on his head that were like mind control.

00:09:09.160 --> 00:09:11.800
It was something with his mind.

00:09:13.560 --> 00:09:18.813
I saw three demons standing behind him influencing his mind.

00:09:21.690 --> 00:09:30.245
It was demonic, a pull on him because he has talent and the enemy knows it.

00:09:43.645 --> 00:09:43.870
The enemy will try to derail what God was doing five or six years ago to make him what he is now.

00:09:49.248 --> 00:09:49.592
And the Lord said, 'Brennan, there's a call.

00:09:49.592 --> 00:09:51.057
' "There's a call.

00:09:51.057 --> 00:09:52.796
" The enemy comes immediately, folks.

00:10:01.430 --> 00:10:03.320
And people say, "Well, Brandon, is that the one you're trying to tell us to watch out for?

00:10:03.320 --> 00:10:07.393
" No, it's one with even greater influence than him.

00:10:23.500 --> 00:10:30.994
The person that I saw that would come out and start preaching that they got born again and have a universal gospel has more influence than Kanye, Katy, and Justin all combined.

00:10:30.994 --> 00:10:34.200
That's how big this person was.

00:10:46.440 --> 00:10:50.760
And I was like, "Wow," because I saw the plan, but it was about snaring the young people.

00:10:56.450 --> 00:10:57.630
It wasn't—like I said, the Lord told me, "Know those that labor among you.

00:10:57.630 --> 00:11:12.135
You're not judging people, but you're watching their fruit and you're not quick to just allow what you know because the young people go, 'Oh my gosh, it's a new Christian celebrity.

00:11:12.135 --> 00:11:13.425
Oh, let's follow it.

00:11:13.425 --> 00:11:41.200
'" And then they get into it and everything looks good for a couple of months, but then everything starts to change and they start preaching there's more than one way to get to the Father other than Jesus Christ.

00:11:44.050 --> 00:11:44.360
But I'm telling you, that is blasphemous.

00:11:44.360 --> 00:11:49.320
There's only one way to the Father and that is Jesus Christ.

00:11:49.320 --> 00:11:50.053
One way.

00:11:53.248 --> 00:11:53.440
The Bible makes that very clear.

00:11:53.440 --> 00:12:13.272
So the Lord showed me a plan, and in this plan of the demonic to try to snare young people to make them think that there's all kinds of different ways to get to the Father.

00:12:13.272 --> 00:12:19.874
That's why it comes out innocent—a spoonful of sugar helps the medicine go down.

00:12:23.760 --> 00:12:24.280
But it's not medicine; it's poison.

00:12:24.280 --> 00:12:28.501
They're going to try to poison you.

00:12:30.244 --> 00:12:38.827
But I just want you to know that the enemy has a plan, but God has a greater plan.

00:12:54.480 --> 00:12:54.800
And we're going to see a great revival, folks.

00:12:54.800 --> 00:13:04.470
But He showed me with this great revival will come great music.

00:13:07.547 --> 00:13:16.540
It won't just be a revival that's normal, like when we get excited about Hillsong and maybe Kari Jobe or whoever.

00:13:16.540 --> 00:13:25.780
There have been some really good ones that have really ministered to me—"The Blessing" and songs like that—but "Oceans" is one of my favorites.

00:13:25.780 --> 00:13:37.920
I know what the Lord has shown me about this next revival, and He's telling me it's time for the body of Christ to pray into this for what's about to take place.

00:13:37.920 --> 00:13:52.427
Heavenly sounds where the music notes dance out of the spirit, and they draw the people in with an anointing that is going to overthrow the status quo of where it is right now.

00:13:53.737 --> 00:14:05.950
The devil's crowd will become God's crowd that's main and center because He's drawing the celebrities that have the talent.

00:14:07.498 --> 00:14:25.300
The devil makes them sign their life contracts, saying, "Well, you sell your soul to me and I'll make you rich," and all the things that he tried to promise me.

00:14:25.300 --> 00:14:58.156
If everybody remembers all that, when he comes and presents all this to you and says, "If you follow me, if you worship me, if you do this, I'll give you this," and they go along the road of that, he totally takes that gift that God gave them and uses it for himself.

00:15:01.829 --> 00:15:02.297
But the Lord said, "Brandon, I'm about to turn the tables.

00:15:02.297 --> 00:15:11.506
You're about to see something you've never seen before in the music industry.

00:15:13.535 --> 00:15:31.360
" And as I was sitting there listening to that hum in that sandwich shop today, waiting on my sandwich, I was humming it and I could feel the anointing.

00:15:31.360 --> 00:15:38.120
And the Lord said, "I'm going to impart giftings of worship on people who are looking for them, Brandon.

00:15:38.120 --> 00:15:52.589
" So if you have a heart for worship, if you have a heart to praise our Father, there are impartations of giftings of heavenly sound coming to the body of Christ.

00:15:56.300 --> 00:15:56.496
And it started today.

00:15:56.496 --> 00:16:04.620
The Lord showed me; I want you to have an expectation for these gifts, to ask the Father, "Give me the heavenly sounds.

00:16:04.620 --> 00:16:08.752
Give me the heavenly worship so I can worship You greater.

00:16:08.752 --> 00:16:27.484
" Not so I can have a Dove Award, or have my name in black and white all over the place where they say, "Well, he's number one in the charts," but just to give You glory.

00:16:27.484 --> 00:16:35.413
Talent brings those things, but the anointing, I'm telling you, breaks the yoke.

00:16:39.190 --> 00:16:39.460
Heavenly sounds and heavenly worship are coming.

00:16:39.460 --> 00:16:44.010
But I saw an impartation for a great turnaround—a divine reversal.

00:16:44.010 --> 00:16:46.559
See, there are words I don't use.

00:16:46.559 --> 00:16:50.600
That's why I ask Him all the time, "Who talks that way?

00:16:50.600 --> 00:16:53.640
" because I ask, "What is a divine reversal?

00:16:55.196 --> 00:16:55.640
" I even write these things out.

00:16:56.725 --> 00:16:58.100
The Lord said, "A divine reversal is coming.

00:16:58.100 --> 00:17:00.240
" I'm changing the status quo.

00:17:02.093 --> 00:17:09.280
I have to go and Google it because I have no idea what He's saying because I don't talk that way.

00:17:09.280 --> 00:17:11.800
I'm such a country boy.

00:17:12.194 --> 00:17:14.166
But I hear it and Braden goes, "What?

00:17:17.360 --> 00:17:17.618
" and writes it down.

00:17:21.451 --> 00:17:24.389
And so, we have to take time to study what the Lord is saying.

00:17:24.389 --> 00:17:28.399
But I want you to be encouraged tonight.

00:17:28.399 --> 00:17:34.560
If you have a heart for worship, there are heavenly sounds coming.

00:17:34.560 --> 00:17:37.229
Catch it!

00:17:37.229 --> 00:17:50.720
Pull it out of the spirit realm and bring it into the natural.

00:17:50.720 --> 00:17:54.542
Have your catcher's mitts on.

00:17:55.249 --> 00:17:58.470
I was humming a tune I've never heard before; the tune was heavenly.

00:18:02.000 --> 00:18:02.600
And the girl with pink hair was listening.

00:18:10.364 --> 00:18:10.693
I got in the car and told Braden, "Get the recorder out.

00:18:14.011 --> 00:18:15.147
I have a tune humming out of the throne.

00:18:15.147 --> 00:18:20.330
" I was humming this tune—I don't know what the words were, but it was heavenly to me.

00:18:22.120 --> 00:18:26.335
I could see the hum had glory on it.

00:18:33.680 --> 00:18:37.164
The Lord said, "There will be more; there are more sounds.

00:18:48.107 --> 00:18:48.440
" So, I've said enough about that, but it went alongside what we prayed about last night concerning Katy Perry.

00:18:48.440 --> 00:19:07.987
I believe that God is about to do something with that woman and with others, where people who were in the dark turn to the light and use their gifts and talents for Jesus.

00:19:07.987 --> 00:19:15.265
That's the whole purpose—giving all the glory to Jesus and telling of His wonderful love.

00:19:28.219 --> 00:19:28.749
Thank you, Jesus.

00:19:28.749 --> 00:19:47.804
I got excited about it and wanted to tell you this afternoon when I got my lunch, but I thought I'd wait and let it marinate for a little bit and pray over it.

00:19:47.804 --> 00:19:58.947
I've had time to think and it's late now.

00:20:07.520 --> 00:20:10.789
I told Braden I should have done it back then because I felt the anointing on it when I was hearing it for the first time.

00:20:13.560 --> 00:20:15.800
I want you to have an expectation to catch it.

00:20:18.058 --> 00:20:19.957
It's all about intimacy with the Father in worship.

00:20:34.180 --> 00:20:39.320
I sing these songs and spend time with Him; it's all about sitting at His feet and bringing people into a place of worship so that they can sit at His feet.

00:20:39.320 --> 00:20:43.910
In His presence, there's fullness of joy and fullness of peace.

00:20:43.910 --> 00:20:46.860
Every time I go to the healing services...

00:20:46.860 --> 00:20:49.080
Bruce and Lisa—thank you, son.

00:20:49.080 --> 00:20:49.980
" Good job.

00:20:49.980 --> 00:21:01.920
Bruce and Lisa will sing, and all of a sudden the glory comes in, and Lisa is anointed.

00:21:01.920 --> 00:21:08.772
When you hear somebody who has a gift that is anointed, it changes the atmosphere.

00:21:08.772 --> 00:21:16.406
There's something about it: heavenly sounds versus somebody who has a gift that's polished for Jesus.

00:21:16.406 --> 00:21:21.228
That's what the Lord was saying: "I'm bringing those gifts on the people.

00:21:21.228 --> 00:21:23.273
" I said, "I receive one.

00:21:23.273 --> 00:21:33.370
Anoint me in another capacity to help you with worship, Lord.

00:21:33.370 --> 00:21:41.887
" I know I never will do a record deal; I don't care about all that.

00:21:41.887 --> 00:21:45.027
You can feel it.

00:21:47.000 --> 00:21:48.340
When praises go up, blessings come down.

00:22:00.970 --> 00:22:01.160
The blessing is a flow of the glory in the atmosphere to change things.

00:22:01.160 --> 00:22:06.320
That's why I love the blessing song Kari Jobe sings.

00:22:15.520 --> 00:22:21.080
I wanted to encourage you all today because there are some of you that are really into music like me.

00:22:21.080 --> 00:22:26.393
I listen to music all day.

00:22:26.393 --> 00:22:26.760
I love music.

00:22:26.760 --> 00:22:34.800
I love to hear Kim Clement's old music when he's singing prophetically at his piano, and he plays those sounds.

00:22:34.800 --> 00:22:41.987
He can hit a certain key on his piano, and it just pulls me in.

00:22:41.987 --> 00:23:00.275
I'll even tell Braden, "I want you to get a loop, and I want you to play that sound throughout the house continually.

00:23:00.275 --> 00:23:21.343
" I want it played throughout the house on our little speaker; I want to listen to it and put it on a loop because certain frequencies and certain sounds bring certain levels of the glory.

00:23:21.343 --> 00:23:23.800
It's by worship.

00:23:23.800 --> 00:23:34.630
If you want to get yourself right into the throne room, it's by worship.

00:23:49.686 --> 00:23:50.057
But there are certain frequencies of sound that bring in that presence.

00:23:50.057 --> 00:24:03.667
Even whenever Sister Billie, remember when we were at the Prayer Mountain Assembly, they were singing a phrase about the glory.

00:24:03.667 --> 00:24:13.857
As this certain sound was coming, you could feel the glory fill the atmosphere.

00:24:13.857 --> 00:24:26.120
I said, "My goodness, all kinds of frequencies of sounds, the way He created us.

00:24:26.120 --> 00:24:36.368
" God is a God of music, worship, and praise.

00:24:39.314 --> 00:24:39.560
And there are sounds—heavenly sounds.

00:24:57.582 --> 00:24:57.778
I'm telling you by the spirit of God, there's a level of worship that we've never seen before for this next end-time glorious church.

00:25:13.547 --> 00:25:14.133
There's another level of sound, keys on the piano, symphonies, and beautiful things from the throne room that will bring us into that level because we're all talking about the glory.

00:25:14.133 --> 00:25:32.854
We're talking about the former and the latter rain and the next Azusa Street revival, not just in one place, but sporadically all throughout the world.

00:25:33.029 --> 00:25:45.480
The Lord said, "I'm getting the sounds ready for that revival and this next outpouring, for it will be sustained through worship.

00:25:46.350 --> 00:25:51.143
" Do you want to change?

00:25:51.143 --> 00:25:54.560
Do you want to have the glory?

00:25:54.560 --> 00:26:07.600
Do you want to see what we're about to see?

00:26:25.552 --> 00:26:25.976
It will come through worship and praise.

00:26:31.360 --> 00:26:34.429
We're wanting to see arms and legs and people's lives changed from glory to glory.

00:26:34.429 --> 00:26:40.320
He's changing us, but it will come through worship, ladies and gentlemen.

00:26:40.320 --> 00:27:17.520
I'm telling you, the Lord said as of today, "I am distributing all the gifts for worship for this revival that's about to take place to make sure it stays in the atmosphere because that is how it changes.

00:27:28.455 --> 00:27:42.980
" Just like I'm talking about Bruce and Lisa, when you're in the healing service of Billie Burke and you see these things and the glory comes in, it comes through the worship.

00:27:42.980 --> 00:27:45.383
I believe in miracles.

00:27:45.383 --> 00:27:53.405
Kathryn Kuhlman and the others—it all went through worship with Dino.

00:27:53.405 --> 00:27:56.400
I'm just trying to tell you what I'm saying.

00:27:58.600 --> 00:28:04.230
A lot of people ask, "What does it take to get over there?

00:28:23.560 --> 00:28:23.897
" When I hear Kim Clement and he plays on the piano, it's certain notes and sounds coming.

00:28:23.897 --> 00:28:29.074
Catch them; you'll birth them out of prayer.

00:28:29.074 --> 00:28:45.360
What happens in the spirit will happen in the natural, but you have to birth it through prayer and fellowship with Him, sitting at His feet.

00:28:49.560 --> 00:28:49.840
The Lord said, "There's intimacy, Brandon.

00:28:49.840 --> 00:28:52.640
Do you see it?

00:28:52.640 --> 00:29:03.000
There's worship and heavenly sounds that you know not of, found by sitting at My feet.

00:29:03.000 --> 00:29:28.880
" There's so much distraction and so many things that preoccupy our attention—our phones, social media—but there is a place in God with this worship that changes the atmosphere so that healings will manifest like we're asking for: the legs, arms, backs, and deliverances where demons flee.

00:29:28.880 --> 00:29:32.090
It's bringing Him into the atmosphere.

00:29:32.090 --> 00:29:38.060
He is beautiful beyond description, too marvelous for words, too wonderful for comprehension, like nothing ever seen or heard.

00:29:38.060 --> 00:29:40.475
Who can grasp Your infinite wisdom?

00:29:40.475 --> 00:29:43.600
Who can fathom the depth of Your love?

00:29:46.640 --> 00:29:47.071
You are beautiful beyond description; it changes the atmosphere.

00:29:50.782 --> 00:29:51.831
That's why it's about going into that throne room.

00:29:54.684 --> 00:29:57.640
It was exciting for me to go over this with you because we're getting so close.

00:29:57.640 --> 00:30:13.320
The music is laying the foundation for what's about to take place, and He's getting His church ready for the ones that are listening.

00:30:13.320 --> 00:30:14.040
Catch it.

00:30:27.080 --> 00:30:27.480
Be a contender.

00:30:27.480 --> 00:30:34.880
That's the word He used with me all the time: "Be a contender.

00:30:34.880 --> 00:30:39.320
Fight for it.

00:30:43.373 --> 00:30:43.560
" Don't just sit there and have a lackadaisical attitude.

00:30:43.560 --> 00:30:53.200
No, how bad do you want it and how bad are you going to fight for it?

00:30:54.640 --> 00:30:59.667
I want the manifested presence of my Father in my house, in my car, and in my church.

00:31:03.320 --> 00:31:09.773
When I go to the grocery store, if I can hum a song in the sandwich shop, if He be lifted up, He'll draw all men unto Him.

